== Overview ==

Dragon Quest I & II for SNES contains items from both Dragon Quest I and Dragon Quest II. This page documents all items and equipment.

== Item Data Structure ==

Each item entry is 8 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Item ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || Item type
|-
| $02 || 1 || Effect value
|-
| $03 || 1 || Equip flags
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Buy price
|-
| $06-$07 || 2 || Sell price
|}

